    <title>Markdown-基本撰写和语法格式</title>
    <link href="/2025/05/28/Markdown-%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%92%B0%E5%86%99%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F/"/>
    <url>/2025/05/28/Markdown-%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%92%B0%E5%86%99%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-标题-章节"><a href="#1-标题-章节" class="headerlink" title="1.标题&#x2F;章节"></a>1.标题&#x2F;章节</h1><h2 id="1-1层级"><a href="#1-1层级" class="headerlink" title="1.1层级"></a>1.1层级</h2><p><strong>如下图所示，共6级依次递进</strong></p><p><img src="/./img/%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%92%B0%E5%86%99%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F-%E5%B1%82%E7%BA%A7%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B.webp" alt="层级示例"></p><p><strong>层级6从属于层级5从属于层级4…每创建一个层级会生成相应定位点以便预览大纲快速跳转</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-section"># 层级1</span><span class="hljs-section">## 层级2</span><span class="hljs-section">### 层级3</span><span class="hljs-section">#### 层级4</span><span class="hljs-section">##### 层级5</span><span class="hljs-section">###### 层级6</span></code></pre></div><h1 id="2-文本样式"><a href="#2-文本样式" class="headerlink" title="2.文本样式"></a>2.文本样式</h1><h2 id="2-1大小"><a href="#2-1大小" class="headerlink" title="2.1大小"></a>2.1大小</h2><p><strong>如下所示，共7级依次递进</strong></p><p><font size=7>永远相信美好的事情即将发生</font></p><p><font size=6>永远相信美好的事情即将发生</font></p><p><font size=5>永远相信美好的事情即将发生</font></p><p><font size=4>永远相信美好的事情即将发生</font></p><p><font size=3>永远相信美好的事情即将发生</font></p><p><font size=2>永远相信美好的事情即将发生</font></p><p><font size=1>永远相信美好的事情即将发生</font></p><p><strong>Size&#x3D;7大于Size&#x3D;6大于Size&#x3D;5…</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">size</span>=<span class="hljs-string">7</span>&gt;</span></span>永远相信美好的事情即将发生<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">size</span>=<span class="hljs-string">6</span>&gt;</span></span>永远相信美好的事情即将发生<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">size</span>=<span class="hljs-string">5</span>&gt;</span></span>永远相信美好的事情即将发生<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">size</span>=<span class="hljs-string">4</span>&gt;</span></span>永远相信美好的事情即将发生<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">size</span>=<span class="hljs-string">3</span>&gt;</span></span>永远相信美好的事情即将发生<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">size</span>=<span class="hljs-string">2</span>&gt;</span></span>永远相信美好的事情即将发生<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">size</span>=<span class="hljs-string">1</span>&gt;</span></span>永远相信美好的事情即将发生<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><div class="note note-info">            <p>Note<br><strong>Size&gt;7最终将以Size&#x3D;7显示</strong></p>          </div><h2 id="2-2加粗-斜体"><a href="#2-2加粗-斜体" class="headerlink" title="2.2加粗&amp;斜体"></a>2.2加粗&amp;斜体</h2><p><strong>加粗</strong></p><p><strong>ABC</strong>比ABC要粗些</p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-strong">**ABC**</span></code></pre></div><p><strong>斜体</strong></p><p><em>ABC</em>是ABC的斜体</p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-emphasis">*ABC*</span></code></pre></div><div class="note note-info">            <p>Note<br><strong>全部加粗及为斜体</strong></p><p><em><strong>ABC</strong></em>不仅加粗还是斜体</p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-strong">**<span class="hljs-emphasis">*ABC*</span>**</span></code></pre></div><p><strong>全部加粗部分斜体</strong></p><p><strong>AB<em>CD</em>EF</strong>全部加粗但<em><strong>CD</strong></em>为斜体</p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-strong">**AB<span class="hljs-emphasis">*CD*</span>EF**</span></code></pre></div><p><strong>全部斜体部分加粗</strong></p><p><em>AB<strong>CD</strong>EF</em>全部为斜体但<em><strong>CD</strong></em>加粗</p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-emphasis">*AB<span class="hljs-strong">**CD**</span>EF*</span></code></pre></div>          </div><h2 id="2-3上标-下标"><a href="#2-3上标-下标" class="headerlink" title="2.3上标&amp;下标"></a>2.3上标&amp;下标</h2><p><strong>上标</strong></p><p>AB<sup>CD</sup>EF中的CD更高</p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例AB<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">sup</span>&gt;</span></span>CD<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">sup</span>&gt;</span></span>EF</code></pre></div><p><strong>下标</strong></p><p>AB<sub>CD</sub>EF中的CD更低</p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例AB<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">sub</span>&gt;</span></span>CD<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">sub</span>&gt;</span></span>EF</code></pre></div><h2 id="2-4删除线-下划线"><a href="#2-4删除线-下划线" class="headerlink" title="2.4删除线&amp;下划线"></a>2.4删除线&amp;下划线</h2><p><strong>删除线</strong></p><p><del>我喜欢她</del>但我更喜欢无畏的自己</p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例~~我喜欢她~~但我更喜欢无畏的自己</code></pre></div><p><strong>下划线</strong></p><p><ins>这很重要，划重点</ins></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ins</span>&gt;</span></span>这很重要，划重点<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">ins</span>&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><h1 id="3-文本颜色"><a href="#3-文本颜色" class="headerlink" title="3.文本颜色"></a>3.文本颜色</h1><h2 id="3-1前景色"><a href="#3-1前景色" class="headerlink" title="3.1前景色"></a>3.1前景色</h2><p><strong>使用颜色名称格式</strong></p><p><font color="red">RED-红色</font></p><p><font color="green">GREEN-绿色</font></p><p><font color="blue">BLUE-蓝色</font></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs html">代码示例<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">color</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;RED&quot;</span>&gt;</span>RED-红色<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">color</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;green&quot;</span>&gt;</span>GREEN-绿色<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">color</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;blue&quot;</span>&gt;</span>BLUE-蓝色<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span></code></pre></div><div class="note note-info">            <p>Note<br><strong>使用HEX格式</strong></p><p><font color="#FF0000">RED-红色</font></p><p><font color="#008000">GREEN-绿色</font></p><p><font color="#0000FF">BLUE-蓝色</font></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs html">代码示例<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">color</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;#FF0000&quot;</span>&gt;</span>RED-红色<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">color</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;#008000&quot;</span>&gt;</span>GREEN-绿色<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">color</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;#0000FF&quot;</span>&gt;</span>BLUE-蓝色<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span></code></pre></div>          </div><h2 id="3-2背景色"><a href="#3-2背景色" class="headerlink" title="3.2背景色"></a>3.2背景色</h2><p><strong>使用颜色名称格式</strong></p><p><font color="#FFFFFF"><font style="background: red">RED-红色</font></font></p><p><font color="#FFFFFF"><font style="background: green">GREEN-绿色</font></font></p><p><font color="#FFFFFF"><font style="background: blue">BLUE-蓝色</font></font></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs html">代码示例<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;background: red&quot;</span>&gt;</span>RED-红色<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;background: green&quot;</span>&gt;</span>GREEN-绿色<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;background: blue&quot;</span>&gt;</span>BLUE-蓝色<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span></code></pre></div><div class="note note-info">            <p>Note<br><strong>使用HEX格式</strong></p><p><font color="#FFFFFF"><font style="background: #FF0000">RED-红色</font></font></p><p><font color="#FFFFFF"><font style="background: #008000">GREEN-绿色</font></font></p><p><font color="#FFFFFF"><font style="background: #0000FF">BLUE-蓝色</font></font></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs html">代码示例<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;background: #FF0000&quot;</span>&gt;</span>RED-红色<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;background: #008000&quot;</span>&gt;</span>GREEN-绿色<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;background: #0000FF&quot;</span>&gt;</span>BLUE-蓝色<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span></code></pre></div>          </div><div class="note note-success">            <p>Tip<br><strong>同时更改前景色与背景色</strong><br><font style="background: #1F883D"><font color="#ffb000">Live at ease like a carrot!</font></font></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs html">代码示例<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;background: #1F883D&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">font</span> <span class="hljs-attr">color</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;#ffb000&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Live at ease like a carrot!<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">font</span>&gt;</span></code></pre></div>          </div><h1 id="4-引用"><a href="#4-引用" class="headerlink" title="4.引用"></a>4.引用</h1><h2 id="4-1引用文本"><a href="#4-1引用文本" class="headerlink" title="4.1引用文本"></a>4.1引用文本</h2><p><strong>右侧灰色索引及垂直线，字体为灰色</strong></p><blockquote><p>Calin的网名是隔壁萝卜</p></blockquote><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例&gt;Calin的网名是隔壁萝卜</code></pre></div><h2 id="4-2引用代码"><a href="#4-2引用代码" class="headerlink" title="4.2引用代码"></a>4.2引用代码</h2><p><strong>单行代码</strong></p><p><code>sudo -i</code></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs bash">代码示例`<span class="hljs-built_in">sudo</span> -i`</code></pre></div><p><strong>多行代码</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">sudo</span> -iapt updateapt upgrade</code></pre></div><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-code">```</span><span class="hljs-code">sudo -i</span><span class="hljs-code">apt update</span><span class="hljs-code">apt upgrade</span><span class="hljs-code">```</span></code></pre></div><div class="note note-info">            <p>Note<br><strong>代码中含有反引号</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-code">```</span><span class="hljs-code">sudo -i</span><span class="hljs-code">rm -rf /*</span><span class="hljs-code">```</span></code></pre></div><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-section">#若即将引用代码带有反引号且数量&gt;=3，则引用代码书写的反引号数量应+1</span><span class="hljs-code">````</span><span class="hljs-code">```</span><span class="hljs-code">sudo -i</span><span class="hljs-code">rm -rf /*</span><span class="hljs-code">```</span><span class="hljs-code">````</span></code></pre></div>          </div><div class="note note-success">            <p>Tip<br><strong>代码引用语法高亮</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-section">#无语法高亮示例</span>sudo -irm -rf /<span class="hljs-emphasis">*</span></code></pre></div><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#有语法高亮示例</span><span class="hljs-built_in">sudo</span> -i<span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> -rf /*</code></pre></div><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-section">#bash可为其他语言，如C,Java等</span><span class="hljs-code">```bash</span><span class="hljs-code">#有高亮语法示例</span><span class="hljs-code">sudo -i</span><span class="hljs-code">rm -rf /*</span><span class="hljs-code">```</span></code></pre></div>          </div><h2 id="4-3引用头部（仅Github警告样式）"><a href="#4-3引用头部（仅Github警告样式）" class="headerlink" title="4.3引用头部（仅Github警告样式）"></a>4.3引用头部（仅Github警告样式）</h2><p><img src="/./img/Github%E8%AD%A6%E6%8A%A5%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B.webp" alt="Github警报示例"></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-quote">&gt; [!NOTE]</span><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; Useful information that users should know, even when skimming content.</span><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; [!TIP]</span><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; Helpful advice for doing things better or more easily.</span><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; [!IMPORTANT]</span><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; Key information users need to know to achieve their goal.</span><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; [!WARNING]</span><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; Urgent info that needs immediate user attention to avoid problems.</span><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; [!CAUTION]</span><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; Advises about risks or negative outcomes of certain actions.</span></code></pre></div>]]></content>
    
    
