    <title>Markdown-基本撰写和语法格式2</title>
    <link href="/2025/05/28/Markdown-%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%92%B0%E5%86%99%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F2/"/>
    <url>/2025/05/28/Markdown-%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%92%B0%E5%86%99%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-图像表格"><a href="#1-图像表格" class="headerlink" title="1.图像表格"></a>1.图像表格</h1><h2 id="1-1图像"><a href="#1-1图像" class="headerlink" title="1.1图像"></a>1.1图像</h2><p><img src="/./img/%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%92%B0%E5%86%99%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F-%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B.PNG" alt="图像示例"></p><p><strong>当图片存于默认自述文件下级目录时</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-section"># - Desktop</span><span class="hljs-section">#-  README</span><span class="hljs-section">#- 基本撰写和格式语法.md </span><span class="hljs-section">#- assets</span><span class="hljs-section">#- Example.PNG</span>![<span class="hljs-string">图像示例</span>](<span class="hljs-link">./assets/图像示例.PNG</span>)</code></pre></div><p><strong>当图片存放于默认自述文件上级目录中时</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-section"># - Desktop</span><span class="hljs-section">#-  README</span><span class="hljs-section">#- 基本撰写和格式语法.md </span><span class="hljs-section">#- assets</span><span class="hljs-section"># - Example.PNG</span>![<span class="hljs-string">Example</span>](<span class="hljs-link">../Example.PNG</span>)</code></pre></div><h2 id="1-2表格"><a href="#1-2表格" class="headerlink" title="1.2表格"></a>1.2表格</h2><p><strong>无序列表</strong></p><ul><li>洗漱用品</li></ul><ul><li>零食饮料</li></ul><ul><li>柴米油盐</li></ul><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-section">#(-)(<span class="hljs-emphasis">*)(+)表达效果相同，均可</span></span><span class="hljs-emphasis"><span class="hljs-section">- 洗漱用品</span></span><span class="hljs-emphasis"><span class="hljs-section">*</span> 零食饮料</span><span class="hljs-bullet">+</span> 柴米油盐</code></pre></div><p><strong>有序列表</strong></p><ol><li>预订餐厅</li><li>打电话给Calin</li><li>一起用餐</li></ol><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-bullet">1.</span> 预订餐厅<span class="hljs-bullet">2.</span> 打电话给Calin<span class="hljs-bullet">3.</span> 一起用餐</code></pre></div><p><strong>嵌套列表</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs">- User- Calin - Desktop - Bin- Download- Share</code></pre></div><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> User<span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> Calin <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> Desktop <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> Bin<span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> Download<span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> Share</code></pre></div><p><strong>任务列表</strong></p><ul><li><p><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 阅读学习</p></li><li><p><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 外出摄影</p></li><li><p><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 写代码</p></li></ul><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> [x] 阅读学习<span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> [ ] 外出摄影<span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> [ ] 写代码</code></pre></div><p><strong>图示列表</strong></p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">时刻&#x2F;星期</th><th align="center">周日</th><th align="center">周一</th><th align="center">周二</th><th align="center">周三</th><th align="center">周四</th><th align="center">周五</th><th align="center">周六</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">6:00</td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td></tr><tr><td align="center">7:00</td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td></tr><tr><td align="center">8:00</td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-section">#必须先写表头，垂直线(|)相当于表格的边框</span><span class="hljs-section">#若需要出现n列，则需要n+1个垂直线</span><span class="hljs-section">#垂直线中仅文字间空格有效</span>|时刻/星期|周日|周一|周二|周三|周四|周五|周六|<span class="hljs-section">#表头写完后换行以调整表格内文字位置，须输入表头相同个数垂直线</span><span class="hljs-section">#|:--|左对齐，|:-:|居中对齐，|--:|右对齐</span>|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|:-:|<span class="hljs-section">#再次换行以写入新行</span>|6:00|||||||||7:00|||||||||8:00||||||||</code></pre></div><p><strong>序号级别</strong></p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">第一层</th><th align="center">第二层</th><th align="center">第三层</th><th align="center">第四层</th><th align="center">第五层</th><th align="center">第六层</th><th align="center">第七层</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">一、</td><td align="center">（一）</td><td align="center">1.</td><td align="center">（1）</td><td align="center">①</td><td align="center">A.</td><td align="center">a.</td></tr><tr><td align="center">二、</td><td align="center">（二）</td><td align="center">2.</td><td align="center">（2）</td><td align="center">②</td><td align="center">B.</td><td align="center">b.</td></tr><tr><td align="center">三、</td><td align="center">（三）</td><td align="center">3.</td><td align="center">（3）</td><td align="center">③</td><td align="center">C.</td><td align="center">c.</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center">（A）</td><td align="center">（a）</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center">（B）</td><td align="center">（b）</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center">（C）</td><td align="center">（c）</td></tr></tbody></table><h1 id="2-段落-注释"><a href="#2-段落-注释" class="headerlink" title="2.段落&#x2F;注释"></a>2.段落&#x2F;注释</h1><h2 id="2-1分段"><a href="#2-1分段" class="headerlink" title="2.1分段"></a>2.1分段</h2><p><strong>空行</strong></p><p><strong>在编辑器中，连续空取三行，最终将显示空取一行</strong></p><p><strong>水平分割线</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-section">#6个英文连字符</span>------</code></pre></div><h2 id="2-2注释"><a href="#2-2注释" class="headerlink" title="2.2注释"></a>2.2注释</h2><p><strong>Markdown注释</strong></p><p><strong>用于在书写时在代码旁批注，最终不予显示</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例&lt;!-- 恨之入骨，爱之入髓，放下挂念，好好生活 --&gt;</code></pre></div><p><strong>脚注（需渲染器支持）</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例海内[^1]存知己，天涯[^2]若比邻[^3][<span class="hljs-symbol">^1</span>]: <span class="hljs-link">海内：四海之内，即全国各地，古代人认为我国疆土四周环海，所以称天下为四海之内。</span>[<span class="hljs-symbol">^2</span>]: <span class="hljs-link">天涯：天边，这里比喻极远的地方。</span>[<span class="hljs-symbol">^3</span>]: <span class="hljs-link">比邻：并邻，近邻。</span></code></pre></div><h1 id="3-链接-定位点"><a href="#3-链接-定位点" class="headerlink" title="3.链接&#x2F;定位点"></a>3.链接&#x2F;定位点</h1><h2 id="3-1网页链接"><a href="#3-1网页链接" class="headerlink" title="3.1网页链接"></a>3.1网页链接</h2><p><strong>直接链接</strong></p><p><a href="https://cn.bing.com/">https://cn.bing.com</a></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例[<span class="hljs-string">https://cn.bing.com</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cn.bing.com</span>)</code></pre></div><div class="note note-info">            <p>Note</p><p><strong>自定义链接名</strong></p><p><a href="https://cn.bing.com/">微软必应中国</a></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例[<span class="hljs-string">微软必应中国</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cn.bing.com</span>)</code></pre></div><p><strong>自定义链接标题&#x2F;鼠标停滞即显文本</strong></p><p><a href="https://cn.bing.com/" title="浏览器搜索引擎">微软必应中国</a></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-section">#须为英文引号</span>[<span class="hljs-string">微软必应中国</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://cn.bing.com &quot;浏览器搜索引擎&quot;</span>)</code></pre></div>          </div><h2 id="3-2标题-章节链接"><a href="#3-2标题-章节链接" class="headerlink" title="3.2标题&#x2F;章节链接"></a>3.2标题&#x2F;章节链接</h2><p><strong>跳转上一章节<a href="#1-1%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F">1.1图像</a></strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例跳转上一章节[<span class="hljs-string">4.1引用文本</span>](<span class="hljs-link">#4-1引用文本</span>)</code></pre></div><div class="note note-primary">            <p>Important<br><strong>圆括号内不能包含空格、斜杠、点等，须用连字符代替</strong><br><strong>页内级别不同的标题内容一致时，圆括号内依旧保持一个井号</strong><br><strong>最小级可不用加连字符和数字，其上级需标记</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-section"># How to be happy</span><span class="hljs-section">## How to be happy</span><span class="hljs-section">### How to be happy</span>跳转至[<span class="hljs-string">How to be happy</span>](<span class="hljs-link">#-1How-to-be-happy</span>)跳转至[<span class="hljs-string">How to study well</span>](<span class="hljs-link">#-2How to be happy</span>)跳转至[<span class="hljs-string">How to study well</span>](<span class="hljs-link">#How to be happy</span>)</code></pre></div>          </div><h2 id="3-3相对链接"><a href="#3-3相对链接" class="headerlink" title="3.3相对链接"></a>3.3相对链接</h2><p><strong>用于跳转至目录下其他文件</strong></p><div class="note note-primary">            <p>Important<br><strong>用于默认展示的自述文件应存放在根目录</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-section"># - Desktop</span><span class="hljs-section">#- README</span><span class="hljs-section">#- README2</span><span class="hljs-section">#- Next.md</span><span class="hljs-section">#- 基本撰写和格式语法.md </span><span class="hljs-section">#- assets</span>[<span class="hljs-string">打开下一篇文章</span>](<span class="hljs-link">./README2/Next.md</span>)</code></pre></div>          </div><h2 id="3-4自定义定位点"><a href="#3-4自定义定位点" class="headerlink" title="3.4自定义定位点"></a>3.4自定义定位点</h2><p><strong>可用于文内标记跳转而非标题&#x2F;章节</strong></p><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">代码示例<span class="hljs-section"># The Hare and The Tortoise</span>A tortoise and a hare live in the forest. One day, a hare meets a tortoise.He asks the tortoise, ”Hi, tortoise. What are you doing?”“I am running.” The tortoise says.<span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;back-to-read&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span>&gt;</span></span>“Haha! Running? You are too slow! Let’s have a race. I will show you what running is.” The hare laughs at the tortoise.“Ok. I believe I will win.” The tortoise says.So they decide to have a race to see who run faster.[<span class="hljs-string">返回阅读</span>](<span class="hljs-link">#back-to-read</span>)</code></pre></div>]]></content>
    
    
